post0.title: Algea growth rate
post0.content: Which group do these algae species belong to? . These algae species can be devided into 9 groups as below: . . Tip: - To isolate a species, double click on the corresponding legend.- To hide a species, single click on the corresponding legend.- Freely rotate with diversed angles to observe more clearly.- Hover on the point to see the information. . Given the same condition, what species grow faster? . Heatmaps is useful for this visualization. . Inspired by DataViz Battle1 . . Data sourced from "DataViz Battle for the month of January 2018: Visualize the Growth Rates of Algae" organized by *r/dataisbeautiful↩ . |

page3.title: Overview
